high_descs: Turn to your left and walk towards the kitchen sink, stopping at the knife on the floor.
Pick up the knife on the floor.
Walk the rest of the way to the sink.
Cut the head of lettuce in the right, larger sink into slices.
Turn around and go to the stove, to your right.
Place the knife in the fry pan on the back, right burner.
Turn to your right and go back to the large, right sink, the lettuce is in.
Pick up one of the slices of lettuce from the sink.
Turn around and go back to the stove on your right.
Place the slice of lettuce in the pan, on the back, right  burner of the stove.
Pick up the pan containing a knife, and lettuce, from the back right burner of the stove.
Turn around and go to the refrigerator across the room..
Place the pan with the knife and lettuce inside it, on the top right shelf of the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan containing a knife and lettuce in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the sink.
Pick up a knife from the floor in front of the sink.
Go to the sink.
Slice the head of lettuce in the sink.
Walk to the stove.
Set the knife on the back right pan on the stove.
Walk back to the sink.
Pick up a slice of lettuce from the sink.
Bring the lettuce slice to the stove.
Set the lettuce slice on the pan with the knife.
Pick up the pan with the knife and the lettuce slice.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Put the pan with the lettuce and knife in the refrigerator.
anns.task_desc: Put a slice of lettuce in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn left and face the ground at the sink
Grab the knife off of the ground
Move slightly to the left
Cut the cabbage in the sink into slices
Turn around and go to the oven
Put the knife in the pan in the top right stove
Turn right and go to the sink
Grab the slice of cabbage from the sink
Turn around and go to the oven
Put the cabbage in the pan in the top right stove
Grab the pan from the top right stove
Turn around and go to the fridge
Put the pan in the fridge
anns.task_desc: Moving a pan with a knife and sliced cabbage in it in the fridge
